item.title: CVE-2022-22521|2024-08-03T03:14:55.411Z -- miele -- benchmark%20programming%20tool
item.description: In Miele Benchmark Programming Tool with versions Prior to 1.2.71, executable files manipulated by attackers are unknowingly executed with users privileges. An attacker with low privileges may trick a user with administrative privileges to execute these binaries as admin.
